			CANDLEWOOD SUITES EXPERIENCE

Welcome to a more casual kind of longer stay, where you’ll always feel at home, at your best and really productive while on the road.

















Your Spacious Suite
Your Spacious Suite
Your Spacious Suite


Whichever suite you choose, it’ll be spacious, comfortable and complete with everything you need to live, work, and relax while you’re away from home.













Fully Equipped Kitchen
Fully Equipped Kitchen
Fully Equipped Kitchen


Your very own taste of home: Fully equipped kitchens well-stocked with everything a hungry home-chef needs to settle in and start cooking: fridge, stovetop, microwave, plenty of counter space and of course, a dishwasher.





















Outdoor Gazebo Grill
Outdoor Gazebo Grill
Outdoor Gazebo Grill


Everything unwinding should be: Sometimes you just want to stand over our Outdoor Gazebo Grill and let the day slip away. We’ll even lend you grilling utensils. 













Candlewood Cupboard®
Candlewood Cupboard®
Candlewood Cupboard®


Stock up on a variety of breakfast items, beverages, snacks, frozen entrées and more, any time—all on the honor system.

















			Relax Wherever You Go

We often say that our guests feel relaxed from the start, and we like to prove it even more. All of our locations are easily accessible and we’re always opening new hotels, so you can book a spacious suite whenever and wherever it works for you. 
















Coming Soon


As Latin America's first Candlewood Suites, the Candlewood Suites Queretaro-Juriquilla is conveniently located offering easy access to the Soccer Stadium and downtown Queretaro. Visit Queretaro's tourist attractions and historical buildings while experiencing rich culture along with traditional and modern dining, all within Juriquilla.












Discover New Orleans



 Book your stay today.
 
For business or leisure in Louisianna's largest city, stay at our relaxing Avondale- New Orleans hotel. You'll be minutes from food and music in the French Quarter, great sporting events and a variety of local companies












Explore Washington, D.C.



Book your Washington stay.
 
It's easy to see the sights of the U.S. capital with an extended stay at our hotel in Alexandria - Fort Belvoir. You'll be close to everything, from the lovely National Portrait Gallery to grand Washington Monument.













