Candlewood Investment Group :: Candlewood :: About Us









HomeAboutLeadershipStrategyContactLogin






About Us
Candlewood Investment Group, LP is an SEC registeredinvestment manager with approximately $1.5 billion of netassets under management as of December 31, 2016,predominantly in credit-based strategies.
Our clients include corporate and public pension plans, foundations, endowments, banks, insurance companies and high-net-worth individuals. The firm's track record began in 2003 operating within the Credit Suisse Group, and was spun-out to an independent investment advisor in 2010. Today, our firm is fully independent and partner owned with offices in New York City and Rye, NY.  The Candlewood platform includes special situations / event-driven distressed credit and structured credit.  We pursue differentiated portfolios with a general aversion to crowded investments and have a demonstrated ability to source, analyze and structure complex investment opportunities.  Across the platform we focus on value-oriented, process-driven investing with the goal of delivering optimized risk-adjusted returns.
LEADERSHIP



